resources.string: With the next few questions we will help you give quick ballpark estimation of your project price.
Type in your working hours amount estimation for this project
Type in amount of money you charge of one hour - without taxes
Are there any additional costs? Stock photography, music, fuel, paychecks or any other expenses on Your side?
Is it a returning business, friend of yours, small local charity organization? Do you want to give any discount to this client?
